title: CHI Silk Infusion Leave-In Treatment, 12 Ounce
description: Farouk CHI Silk Infusion is specifically developed to work in conjunction with the CHI Styling Tool product lines. CHI Silk Infusion is a rich leave-in-treatment formulated with pure silk, wheat and soy proteins that will penetrate deep.

title: L'Oreal Paris Voluminous Smoldering Eyeliner, Black, 0.087 Ounces
description: L'Oreal, building on the popularity of prestige kajal liners, introduces the first true kajal pencil to the mass market with a custom sharpener. Kajal inspired smoldering liner adds intense black definition to your eye.

title: Covergirl Lip Perfection Lipliner Radiant 230, 0.04-Ounce
description: For fifty years, COVERGIRL has created must-have beauty products that bring out the best in women.
